 and was later formalized through the Dayton Peace Agreement, is an example of a qualifying agreement.\\n\\nAn official unilateral pledge by Ukraine formally recognizing Russian sovereignty over any UN-recognized Ukrainian territory will qualify for a “Yes” resolution even if not part of an agreement with Russia.\\n\\nThe April 19, 2013, Brussels Agreement between Serbia and Kosovo, in which Serbia recognized Kosovo’s de facto administration but did not formally grant de jure recognition, would not be considered a qualifying agreement under this market, as this market requires formal recognition of sovereignty rather than acknowledgment of administrative control.\\n\\nThe primary resolution source for this market will be an official announcement by Ukraine and/or the Russian Federation, however, an overwhelming consensus of credible reporting confirming an agreement has been reached will also qualify.\\n", "feesEnabled": false, "seriesColor": "", "clobTokenIds": "[\\"111407906413483830198481741547621131014289190946534570245645667771579973364067\\", \\"112468620935063687606410022378078855998390735429551163191251582889945981781902\\"]", "liquidityNum": 13582.6876, "negRiskOther": false, "orderMinSize": 5, "startDateIso": "2026-02-03", "submitted_by": "0x91430CaD2d3975766499717fA0D66A78D814E5c5", "liquidityClob": 13582.6876, "outcomePrices": "[\\"0.14\\", \\"0.86\\"]", "showGmpSeries": false, "volume1moClob": 9163.670991, "volume1wkClob": 4884.597145999999, "volume1yrClob": 9644.612128, "customLiveness": 0, "groupItemTitle": "December 31, 2026", "lastTradePrice": 0.14, "rewardsMinSize": 20, "showGmpOutcome": false, "volume24hrClob": 265.72319, "acceptingOrders": true, "enableOrderBook": true, "clearBookOnStart": true, "hasReviewedDates": true, "manualActivation": false, "negRiskRequestID": "", "resolutionSource": "", "rewardsMaxSpread": 3.5, "pendingDeployment": false, "deployingTimestamp": "2026-02-03T15:26:08.528222Z", "groupItemThreshold": "2", "marketMakerAddress":